node.text:
Method to the Madness 🌈🦄✨
When you watch kids play a character they admire, they really believe they are that character. Way before the UFC debut I would spend hours in an enclosed space and visualize what it looked like, what it felt like to experience it all. From the check ins, media scrums, weigh ins, being in the tunnel, walkout, fight, post win interview…etc. “Imaginaaaaation” *Spondgebob voice* is where everything stems from. The stronger you can actively work that superpower daily, the better you will become at manifesting anything.
“oH gRoW uP!”…yea sure do that 🙄 (it’s a trap), but never loose that childlike spark that creates the wonderful world you wanna experience. Keep it playful 👁

The Rake is a master of language, communicative influence, and poetic verbiage. Often times, we may know we aren't going anywhere mature with a Rake, but that's what makes them so attractive. They are the heat of the moment and give us some texture in our They could pull a casanova and hide in a closet until you're alone for the pleasurable dull lives. taking.'.

node.text:
💜✨
Since we just missed NZ Fashion week…
Robe from Op Shop/ Thrift Store ($30)
Watch ($##,800)
Slides ($69.95)
When I used to walk fashion week I always said, the same people lookin at me walking down that runway wouldn’t look at me twice in the street. They are only looking at me because they are told to look at me in that setting. Now I constantly get looked at in the streets by people I’ve never met, like I’m on a runway during fashion week or something lol.
#hobolife #fullcircle ☮️
